{"tid":1689033,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"創興銀行","createTime":"2019-11-02T16:04:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T07:10:44.000Z","uid":52540,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3d960a74b704b953d177eb570ae96a5808945666","tid":1689033,"uid":52540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:04:56.000Z","msg":"前身:1948年，廖創興開辦廖創興儲蓄銀莊，1955年正式註冊為廖創興銀行。1962年，建成位於中區的總行大廈。<br />\n<br />\n2013年10月25日，越秀企業和越秀金融以每股35.69港元（4.6美元、448日圓，以及2.84英鎊）或326,250,000股，收購創興銀行75%股權，總代價為116.44億港元（15億美元、1463億日圓，以及9.29億英鎊），完成後每股可獲得4.5195港元（0.58美元、56日圓，以及0.36英鎊）的現金中期特別股息，同時保留上市地位。<br />\n<br />\n在2014年2月5日，該公司和越秀企業在股東大會，接受收購事項所有上行使的表決權約97.51%（424,169,961股創興銀行股份）。收購完成後，廖創興業將持有創銀已發行股本約11.59%，<br />\n<br />\n2014年12月29日 創興銀行宣佈，全面使用併入越秀集團品牌印記的新標誌 ，代表該行自2014年2月14日成為越秀集團成員後，再邁進一個新里程"},{"pid":"de9ced891950a56c882bad9c02289475a480f188","tid":1689033,"uid":52540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:05:58.000Z","msg":"越秀企業（集團）有限公司，簡稱越秀企業（集團），以及越秀企業（英語：Yuexiu Enterprises（Holdings）Limited），在1985年由廣州市人民政府於香港成立；前身為「越秀企業有限公司」"},{"pid":"ce783048f33471771914b31725ab0372d881ad50","tid":1689033,"uid":52540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:07:03.000Z","msg":"超過30年的改革發展，集團已形成以金融，房地產，交通基建，都市農業為核心產業，造紙，發展等傳統產業和未來可能進入的戰略性新興產業內部 的&ldquo; 4 + X&rdquo;現代產業體系。<br />\n<br />\n截至2019年6月底，集團總資產超過6300億元人民幣； 2019年上半年，集團實現營業收入332億美元，利潤總額89億美元，預計預算利稅總額約230億元。其中，主業資產規模 佔比約96％，營收佔比約95％，利潤貢獻佔比約98％。<br />\n<br />\n越秀集團控有越秀金控，創興銀行，越秀地產，越秀交通基建，越秀房託基金等五家上市公司。集團整體資產證券化率約95％。"},{"pid":"a721bba99af337d9f78f8ae88e4a3accb0b75aeb","tid":1689033,"uid":52540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:08:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">越秀銀行</span></span>"},{"pid":"a877ff374ceffa6111eddf933176e22a4570ade5","tid":1689033,"uid":52540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:09:23.000Z","msg":"創興銀行 全賴<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">越秀集團</span></span> 支持<br />\n得以持續發展"},{"pid":"c80fbd294f6706cca515179416a34f2fb64695c1","tid":1689033,"uid":52540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:10:35.000Z","msg":"自推 睇下邊個想了解創興銀行 歷史"},{"pid":"4a01afe1b9ce220054f018901bd5d29ac73d1ba2","tid":1689033,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:11:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b138e16028ab16e020729e365b8e1598d94273be","tid":1689033,"uid":52540,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4a01afe1b9ce220054f018901bd5d29ac73d1ba2","tid":1689033,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:11:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:12:19.000Z","msg":"由<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">越秀集團</span></span><br />\n全資擁有<br />\n前身為港資"},{"pid":"61bd960910b9239daa03fe85c7a34ee290dc2270","tid":1689033,"uid":52540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:16:31.000Z","msg":"第8推"},{"pid":"f59cca7bf8bad632ed29031327b6c8edd3b9b49c","tid":1689033,"uid":52540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:17:40.000Z","msg":"第9推"},{"pid":"1a0124b4eaeea6cd94120283c7e87002566e0560","tid":1689033,"uid":52540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:19:59.000Z","msg":"最後一推"},{"pid":"8fd7461fae22ee7dd6086129ffb5755782982de2","tid":1689033,"uid":186800,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:47:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想拆咪拆囉 <br />\n拆錯咪講聲sorry 又無後果"},{"pid":"4cbc28b1bba10b66e8fcf3ad8bbbee5996b10025","tid":1689033,"uid":27319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a01afe1b9ce220054f018901bd5